cetus.hir

Class DFIterator<E extends Traversable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • cetus.hir.IRIterator<E>
      • cetus.hir.DFIterator<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<E>

    public class DFIterator<E extends Traversable>
extends IRIterator<E>
    Alternative implementation to DepthFirstIterator, which supports depth-first iteration over a specific type when requested. Unlike DepthFirstIterator, DFIterator does not allocate internal storage to place next items to be searched for; it performs memory-less search by visiting the node in the IR tree to find the next item to be returned.
